**Demo Codebase Characteristics:**
- **Files:** 30 source files + 10 config files
- **Languages:** Python (15), SDF/XML (8), Shell (5), Params (2)
- **Lines of Code:** ~3,500 LOC
- **Complexity:** Multi-system integration (Gazebo, ArduPilot, Python)

**AGENTS.md Metrics:**
